    <h3 class="section-title">Plan Managed NDIS Funding</h3>

    <p>For participants with Plan managed NDIS funding, the process of purchasing through MobilityCare is simple and efficient. Here's how you can get started:</p>

    <h4>Select the Product:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Visit your desired product page.</li>
        <li>Click on the "<strong>Generate Quote</strong>" button located on the product page.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Generate Your Quote:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>After clicking "Generate Quote", fill out the required fields and hit <strong>Submit</strong>.</li>
        <li>A quote will be created based on your selected products and will be emailed to you.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Send the Quote to Your Plan Manager:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Once you receive your quote, send it to your Plan Manager for approval.</li>
        <li>Your Plan Manager will review the quote and confirm whether your NDIS funding can cover the purchase.</li>
        <li>After approval, ask your Plan Manager to send written confirmation to <a href="mailto:admin@mobilitycare.net.au">admin@mobilitycare.net.au</a> to proceed with the order. This ensures that the purchase is processed correctly and in line with your plan.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Required Participant’s Details (to include in the confirmation email):</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Full Name</li>
        <li>NDIS Number</li>
        <li>Date of Birth (necessary for claims in the myplace provider portal)</li>
        <li>Plan Start and End Dates (to ensure the purchase falls within the active plan period)</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Required Plan Manager Details (to include in the confirmation email):</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Plan Manager Full Name</li>
        <li>Plan Manager NDIS Provider Number</li>
        <li>Plan Manager Contact Information (email, phone number)</li>
        <li>Individual Planner's Name and Contact Details (if applicable)</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Payment Process through Your Plan Manager:</h4>
    <p>After the Plan Manager approves the purchase, they will use the myplace provider portal to pay for the goods using your NDIS plan funds.</p>
    <p>If required, you also have the option to pay out of pocket and receive reimbursement from your Plan Manager. This option can help speed up the process if you need the items sooner.</p>

    <h4>Need Assistance?</h4>
    <p>If you need any help throughout this process, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@mobilitycare.net.au">admin@mobilitycare.net.au</a> or consult your Plan Manager for guidance on how to best manage your NDIS funding.</p>
