    <p>For participants with self-managed NDIS funding, you can now purchase your MobilityCare products upfront using a credit or debit card and then claim your funds back through the myplace portal or my NDIS app.</p>

    <h4>How it Works:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Add the products to your cart by clicking "<strong>Buy Now</strong>" on the product page, then complete your purchase using Visa or Mastercard.</li>
